{"tid":1788821,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大洋洲冠軍Hienghene Sport算唔算係2019年最神奇球隊？","createTime":"2019-12-19T03:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T07:47:48.000Z","uid":73381,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be310d654b39c66c0ddc1618bb8e4287cc70bf1a","tid":1788821,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/94/Hyenghene_Sport.png/200px-Hyenghene_Sport.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2F9%2F94%2FHyenghene_Sport.png%2F200px-Hyenghene_Sport.png&h=3493a543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依隊黎自新喀里多尼亞嘅球隊 爆大冷拎咗大洋洲聯賽冠軍杯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0InLECuNyk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0InLECuNyk4&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=c0a04d1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0InLECuNyk4</a><br />\n<br />\n去到世冠 諗住一定比人炒到仆街啦 點知90分鐘可以迫和對手 如果唔係個龍on9 搵手接回傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分分鐘可以晉埋級#adore<br />\n<br />\n留意返隊波幾乎全隊都係新喀里多尼亞本土球員 而新喀里多尼亞嘅FIFA排名係140 同香港差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd82477bd4bea192317d11ac2e5d8ec5a80068e","tid":1788821,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:58:31.000Z","msg":"個龍個款似街場唔夠人 是但搵條友黎守 唔知回傳唔接得咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7e8fb76aa454e33939fe61def77d9b64a4e558","tid":1788821,"uid":59966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"新喀里多尼亞係紐西蘭剋星黎 大溪地贏大洋洲國家杯個屆 就係新喀里多尼亞贏左紐西蘭<br />\n<br />\n今屆大